      <abstract>
        <p>A new Schiff base ester, 3-hydroxy-4-{[(4-methoxyphenyl)imino]methyl}phenyl octadecanoate, was synthesized and its IR, <sup>1</sup>H NMR, <sup>13</sup>C NMR and MS spectroscopic data are presented.</p>
      </abstract>
      <kwd-group>
        <kwd>3-hydroxy-4-{[(4-methoxyphenyl)imino]methyl}phenyl octadecanoate</kwd>
        <kwd>Schiff base</kwd>
        <kwd>alkyl chain</kwd>
      </kwd-group>
